claim.claim-text:
1. A sheet folding up and rolling machine, comprising: 
a frame member having an input tunnel at a side thereof and an output tunnel at the other side thereof; 
a feeding cylinder assembly having at least one feeding cylinder pivoted in said frame member behind said input tunnel for driving a sheet; 
at least five folding cylinders pivoted in said frame member behind said feeding cylinder assembly for the sheet that passes through said feeding cylinder assembly can pass through said folding cylinders continually; 
at least two guiding plates secured in said frame member corresponding to said feeding cylinder assembly and said folding cylinders respectively for guiding the sheet passing through said feeding cylinder assembly and said folding cylinders; 
at least two limiting members secured in said frame member, each of which has an opening facing to said folding cylinders respectively, for the sheet can run into said limiting members and to be bent; 
a pair of rolling cylinders, which are made of metal, pivoted in said frame behind said folding cylinders for rolling the sheet; 
a coupler assembly having a first wheel secured on said feeding cylinder, a second wheel secured on said folding cylinder, a third wheel secured on said rolling cylinder and a coupler belt mounted around said first wheel, said second wheel and said third wheel for driving said feeding cylinder assembly, said folding cylinders and said rolling cylinders to turn, and 
a driving unit disposed at said frame member for driving said coupler belt to turn.
